name: garyhoov_us-religion-by-county
title: US Religion by County
description:
200+ religions, congregations and members or adherents, by county, 2010

This data is from http://www.thearda.com/Archive/ChCounty.asp
It can be used with my election file by county which includes population of each area.
Both files use the FIPS code system for US counties.
See the notes on the election file for more information on that.
The "Codebook" lists the variable names -- lots of data here!
